{"tid":2077180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"速龍小隊不展示編號覆核案 高院今合併處理 陳伯斥警其身不正","createTime":"2020-06-24T05:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T08:15:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"693e064ca03d9c04053742361b7469a054065c89","tid":2077180,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074841\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074841&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=d4adb772\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074841&h=bb334efc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074841</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）高等法院今日（6月24日）合併處理5宗挑戰速龍小隊制服上不顯示警員編號的司法覆核案件。其中一名申請人「守護孩子」成員陳基裘（陳伯）在開庭前批評，警方其身不正，「警察叫人要守法，自己又唔做好！」<br />\n<br />\n陳基裘稱去年6月12日在金鐘被疑似速龍小隊的人士驅趕，期間想用手機拍攝，遭對方喝止，其後想投訴卻找不到其警員編號，遂提出司法覆核。案件申請人是陳基裘，答辯人是香港政府警務處。除了陳基裘外，郭卓堅、通識科教師楊子俊、陳恭信以及香港記者協會去年均有就「速龍小隊」未有展示警員編號申請司法覆核，共5宗案件今日一併審理。"},{"pid":"88e68282179fb237caa33a34e0e1b997b5540e70","tid":2077180,"uid":146737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T05:52:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmbxE55hyYzQ&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=7e06046c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ</a>"},{"pid":"c091d5e197c67858b7bf8d27fa6e0422f8db0668","tid":2077180,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T05:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a849af564e5c1d91ab582767ebfe83cdea7f6963","tid":2077180,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebb40e92eb6984489514bdff163808513af856f","tid":2077180,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f164f5858d1200dcb5b39eb4bb996033e81167","tid":2077180,"uid":4116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afb2259d14211de7ff99b61318717f4ae5e364a","tid":2077180,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真<br />\n屌你老母行得正驚乜鳩呀又<br />\n死黑警"},{"pid":"523b2d8494de99b0ae9e4b2cacf5078f2e5543be","tid":2077180,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9260b53624eeed6744e6e0fe91832339b6a1c85a","tid":2077180,"uid":89063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"唔止速龍"},{"pid":"fa421a4d946bbeda06d03ba9986d7b23b7a8ce61","tid":2077180,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba9b8335785b21c1f09ac947cfce2e86f509e6a3","tid":2077180,"uid":89063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:46:04.000Z","msg":"其實遮晒樣咁都唔得，唔可以習慣"},{"pid":"f5b3a06c3dfd7abfeb6bf616a871e4077bb57fd5","tid":2077180,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T06:46:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"516e3a6a9a54568e8960057148162ef062a6493a","tid":2077180,"uid":279819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:43:40.000Z","msg":"李柱銘指政府無解釋不展示編號做法 似乎想隱瞞事實<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533879-20200624.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533879-20200624.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=fe51d757\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533879-20200624.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d0e188e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533879-20200624.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n高等法院合併處理挑戰警員不展示編號的5宗相關司法覆核案，早上先處理團體「守護孩子」成員陳基裘，和眼部中槍受傷的教師楊子俊的司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n代表他們的資深大律師李柱銘表示，政府一方未有提交文件，解釋警方去年6月改變不再展示編號的做法，質疑政府一方並非開誠佈公，似乎想向法庭隱瞞事實。<br />\n<br />\n李柱銘表示，每名警務人員一直在制服展示獨一無二的編號，但其後的情況猶如達爾文提出的進化論，突然和不斷發生變化，最終連編號都消失。<br />\n<br />\n李柱銘引述保安局局長李家超指，「速龍小隊」工作服沒有位置展示編號，但他質疑，如果工作服沒有位置展示編號，當初為何要大批購入，當局做錯是毋須爭論。"},{"pid":"c6727406cbee8e11a6a02b65879e22d3d5d1e6ca","tid":2077180,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4b2e80877e9992086319079844d11d6fedb5c8","tid":2077180,"uid":149021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfcfca8269752275d436fb87f484a5597172411","tid":2077180,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:49:32.000Z","msg":"［行動post ］［請置頂］G20國請願！簽名師召喚！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2077187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2077187</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9a025db5812a26a70f03c2acda0b4f159599bfae","tid":2077180,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4586b08b2188993ff366d9477b7e657edb26c5","tid":2077180,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed12dfd9980e08c71dfb05bd50326541a8c449e2","tid":2077180,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abfcfca8269752275d436fb87f484a5597172411","tid":2077180,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:49:32.000Z","msg":"［行動post ］［請置頂］G20國請願！簽名師召喚！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2077187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2077187</a><br />\n- 